{"id":"d9f7f82a-548b-49b2-9f02-8928a964fd5e","title":"1551/12/19: To Lionardo di Buonarroto Simoni","type":"main-list-block","children":[{"id":"29f6c00d-a901-49c5-b4d3-fac4b338e43a","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"From Rome, December 19th, 1551.","standoffProperties":[{"id":"3b60d01a-4488-40a3-bebb-d8874b41c538","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":0,"end":3,"value":"8532f2fa-b614-4eed-9eae-586327f6a15a","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"6bb2c553-4151-4966-81a9-07d280d82282","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":5,"end":8,"value":"501a8a32-2c8a-4934-9060-8c7e36339f0f","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"169e9af7-d345-4525-99b2-089597dfa8b5","type":"codex/time-reference","start":11,"end":29,"value":"ab835b7a-fb0a-4770-a3a9-41682182ea2f","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"a43b767d-0e89-42c0-a648-ba8713b75d25","type":"style/superscript","start":22,"end":23,"value":null,"zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]}],"blockProperties":[]},{"id":"13983fec-c593-4d0c-9617-265da12445df","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"To Lionardo di Buonarroto Simoni,","standoffProperties":[{"id":"571a8ddf-4ab8-43c1-b995-4b3923ba9406","type":"style/italics","start":0,"end":31,"value":null,"zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"d75d6bdd-dddf-4bda-a302-1e337604cf7c","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":3,"end":31,"value":"93ce2119-f2b8-4642-b551-7b8ca6b1ed96","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]}],"blockProperties":[]},{"id":"be799d25-9dce-4440-b85c-a6f04f5cae5d","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"in Florence.","standoffProperties":[{"id":"62047187-c641-48ba-9a03-a26a5fcc1cb5","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":3,"end":10,"value":"671ee7e7-ae1b-4a5a-9591-b40203d5108f","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]}],"blockProperties":[]},{"id":"d6f48ea6-80d2-4293-abee-2565d81a2ce1","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"","standoffProperties":[],"blockProperties":[]},{"id":"a25d8b9a-521f-4b7f-8484-e097c0e9e8a6","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"Lionardo,\u00A0\u2014\u00A0Thy last letter tells me about the shortness of sight, which seems to me no small defect. However, my answer is that I have given no promises here, so that if thou likewise hast given no promises\u00A0in Florence I think it would be best to let the matter\u00A0drop if thou art certain that she is short-sighted; for\u00A0as thou sayest, it is a defect that goes by heredity. Once more I would impress upon thee what I have already written on many occasions: thou art to seek out someone who is healthy, more for the love of God than to secure a dowry, provided that she be a good woman and of noble birth. Do not let it trouble thee if she be poor, for then she will bring thee the more tranquillity. On this head I have no more to say. I am an old man and have but little capital, and even that I do not wish to spend here. Therefore, when thou hearest of some house or property which would be a sound investment for the sum of 1,500 crowns, I shall be ready to buy it. Give the matter thine attention, therefore, so that if I were to die here\u00A0\u2014\u00A0as may happen any day\u00A0\u2014\u00A0the money may not be lost to thee.","standoffProperties":[{"id":"599b4161-f576-41d1-b75b-a7db175d5faa","type":"style/uppercase","start":0,"end":7,"value":null,"zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"e9a84efa-d5a6-46c6-b017-66e88bd13143","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":0,"end":7,"value":"93ce2119-f2b8-4642-b551-7b8ca6b1ed96","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"b725cf26-724a-4fc0-a903-bcbb52b299b0","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":12,"end":14,"value":"93ce2119-f2b8-4642-b551-7b8ca6b1ed96","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"28c732b0-3fbf-4c04-a34e-4d1ffcf17f4f","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":21,"end":26,"value":"d4068b06-6671-432b-907f-8d05b20ef8fd","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"7caf5666-526a-4b05-9011-cec31a5dee49","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":34,"end":35,"value":"add92e01-cefe-4f13-94dd-f00eb82155b0","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"i